Class BatchRequest

java.lang.Object
  com.restfb.batch.BatchRequest

public class BatchRequest
extends Object

Encapsulates a discrete part of an entire Facebook Batch API request.

Must be constructed by BatchRequest.BatchRequestBuilder.

1.6.5
